![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8d67569d-d8e0-404d-baa8-13f6b7e66af7/20240826_200658.jpg)

*   ## **_UNCLE HOWDY DEF. CHAD GABLE_**
    

Bo Dallas returns to the ring for the first time since Bray Wyatt's passing. He looked GREAT and did not miss a step.

American Made runs interference while the ref is out until the rest of the Wyatt6 fight them off.

Howdy wins with a BEAUTIFUL Sister Abigail.